## Truth Engine — Semantic Colours
RESERVED for match/risk indicators ONLY. Never decorative.
- Emerald (Safe/Match): text-emerald-400 bg-emerald-500/10 border-emerald-500/25
- Amber (Warning/Caution): text-amber-400 bg-amber-500/10 border-amber-500/25
- Rose (Risk/Reject): text-rose-400 bg-rose-500/10 border-rose-500/25

